## ğŸ§ª Sample Mini Project (Certification-Aligned)

### ğŸ”¹ Project: Python-Based Network Configuration Automation

**Problem Statement:**  
Manually configuring multiple network devices is time-consuming and error-prone. This mini project automates configuration tasks using Python.

**Project Scope:**
- Read device details from configuration files or a database
- Simulate network configuration changes using Python scripts
- Implement logging and structured error handling
- Store execution results in an open-source database

**Skills Demonstrated:**
- Python fundamentals & OOP
- File handling and data processing
- Automation workflow design
- Basic database interaction

This project directly reinforces **certification objectives** while reflecting **real-world network automation scenarios**.

